      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Siri creates an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/sirikit/insendpaymentintent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object when the current user asks to transfer money to another user. A send payment intent object includes the payment amount and the recipient of the payment. Use that information to validate the transaction and transfer the funds. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To handle this intent, the handler object in your Intents extension must adopt the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/sirikit/insendpaymentintenthandling"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol. Your handler should confirm the request and create an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/sirikit/insendpaymentintentresponse"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object with the result of sending the money to the specified user."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This intent object represents a financial transaction between two users."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Additional Intent Attributes",
          "anchor": "2528231"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/sirikit/insendpaymentintent#2132403"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " lists additional attributes of this intent object. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
