            ]
          ],
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "2132403",
            "title": "Table 1",
            "abstract": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Send payment intent attributes"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When performing a search, Siri automatically asks the user to unlock a currently locked device. You don’t need to explicitly ask to unlock the device. In addition, Siri always prompts the user to confirm the payment before asking your Intents extension to handle the transaction."
            }
